name: Morgue - Death On Top Series 03
description:
Swallow swallow, pretty bird: children play twisting your head. Poking fingers in your belly, boy oh boy, you sure are smelly.

 The midnight caller at the steps has been called to take the dead. Are you ready my dear child? Said the caller and then smiled.

Calling all the in-betweeners: bloated skin, breath seldom fresh. Our rotten parts have come together, no preservation of the flesh!

Did you also get that feeling? A fleeting something you can’t grasp? Something rather unappealing growing under/inside us.

Carve a line across your sixpack, let the gas inside you flow! So much time metiendo panza, now’s your chance to let it go. Fight the need for quiet torment, let your anguish out with stench! All that heartbreak and affliction better out that in your chest. 

Have you felt like you lost something? Now’s the time to go and take. Take the meat that’s on the table, have dessert tall in your bed! Eat each other, oh so tender: let me blow your fucking brrrrains! 

Welcome, welcome, in-betweeners: to the waging age of rage! If you thought your days were over, welcome to this broken stage! Now the cage no longer bounds you, you won’t have to act your age! So let me lick your salty fingers, go and nib on my left toe, let us use our tongues for drinking all these juices from our holes.

KILL COUNT +8
